        String subscribe(String topic,
               String notificationsEndPoint)
        Subscribe to a topic at the endpoint in AbstractReceiverRest.AbstractReceiverRest(String). The callback will be used by the DSB to send the subscriptions. It is your responsibility to prevent/avoid duplicate subscriptions if needed.
        Parameters:
        topic -
        notificationsEndPoint - callback SOAP URI to receive notifications
        Returns:
        subscription ID as URI resource
